#OHJE_S  
Additional codes for specification of free graft of muscle, tendon, fascia, periosteum, perichondrium or cartilage, free microvascular grafts, and flaps (including flaps of bone, muscle and skin), see
Tissue procurement for transplantation, see: Chapter Y
#OHJE_R

#OHJE_S  
Additional codes for specification of free graft of muscle, tendon, fascia, periosteum, perichondrium or cartilage, free microvascular grafts, and flaps (including flaps of bone, muscle and skin), see
Tissue procurement for transplantation, see: Chapter Y
#OHJE_R

#ENGL

#OHJE_S  
Additional codes for specification of free graft of muscle, tendon, fascia, periosteum, perichondrium or cartilage, free microvascular grafts, and flaps (including flaps of bone, muscle and skin), see
Tissue procurement for transplantation, see: Chapter Y

#OHJE_S  
Additional codes for specification of free graft of muscle, tendon, fascia, periosteum, perichondrium or cartilage, free microvascular grafts, and flaps (including flaps of bone, muscle and skin), see
Tissue procurement for transplantation, see: Chapter Y

#ENGL       
#OHJE_S

#OHJE_R

#OHJE_S

Tissue procurement for transplantation, see: Chapter Y

#OHJE_S  
Additional codes for specification of free graft of muscle, tendon, fascia, periosteum, perichondrium or cartilage, free microvascular grafts, and flaps (including flaps of bone, muscle and skin), see
Tissue procurement for transplantation, see: Chapter Y
#OHJE_R
